\c 44
\s Josefa anoidza madzikoma ake
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakaraira mutariri weimba yake, achiti: Zadza masaga evarume nekudya, sezvavanogona kutakura, uisewo mari yemurume umwe neumwe pamuromo wesaga rake.
\v 2 Nemukombe wangu, mukombe wesirivha, uise pamuromo wesaga remudukusa, nemari yake yezviyo. Iye ndokuita zvichienderana neshoko Josefa raakange ataura.
\v 3 Mangwanani kwaedza varume vakatenderwa kuenda, ivo nembongoro dzavo.
\v 4 Vakati vabuda muguta, vasati vaenda kure, Josefa ndokuti kumutariri weimba yake: Simuka, tevera varume; zvino kana wavabata, uti kwavari: Sei manditsindika?
\v 5 Hausi iwo unonwirwa naishe wangu, newaanoshopera nawo here? Maita chakaipa, nezvamaita.
\p
\v 6 Zvino wakavabata, ndokutaura kwavari mashoko iyawa.
\v 7 Zvino vakati kwaari: Ishe wangu anotaurirei mashoko akadai? Ngazvisadaro, varanda venyu havangaiti chinhu ichi.
\v 8 Tarirai, mari yatakawana pamiromo yemasaga edu takadzosa kubva kunyika yeKenani; taigoba sei kubva mumba maishe wako sirivha kana goridhe?
\v 9 Ani nani wevaranda venyu anowanikwa anawo, ngaafe; nesu tichava vasungwa vashe wangu.
\p
\v 10 Iye ndokuti, Ikozvinowo, ngazvive semashoko enyu; iye anowanikwa anawo, achava nhapwa yangu; asi imwi muchava vasina mhosva.
\v 11 Zvino vakakurumidza umwe neumwe kuburutsira saga rake pasi, umwe neumwe ndokusunungura saga rake.
\v 12 Iye ndokutsvaka, akatanga kumukurusa, ndokuguma kumudukusa; mukombe ndokuwanikwa musaga raBhenjamini.
\v 13 Zvino vakabvarura nguvo dzavo, umwe neumwe ndokutakudza mbongoro yake, ndokudzokera kuguta.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Judha nevana vababa vake vakasvika kuimba yaJosefa, nokuti iye wakange achirimo, zvino vakawira pasi pamberi pake.
\v 15 Zvino Josefa wakati kwavari: Chiitoi ichi chamaita? Hamuzivi kuti zvirokwazvo munhu wakaita seni anogona kushopera here?
\p
\v 16 Judha ndokuti: Tichatii kuna ishe wangu? Tichataurei? kana tichazvichenesa sei? Mwari wakawana kutadza kwevaranda venyu tarirai tiri nhapwa kuna ishe wangu, zvose isu naiye muruoko rwake makawanikwa mukombe.
\p
\v 17 Iye ndokuti: Ngazvisadaro, handingaiti saizvozvo; murume muruoko rwake muchawanikwa mukombe uchava nhapwa yangu; asi kana muri imwi, endai nerugare kuna baba venyu.
\p
\v 18 Judha ndokuswedera kwaari, ndokuti: Haiwa, ishe wangu, Regai henyu muranda wenyu ataure shoko munzeve dzaishe wangu, uye kutsamwa kwenyu ngakurege kupfutira muranda wenyu, nokuti imwi makaita saFarao.
\v 19 Ishe wangu wakabvunza varanda vake, achiti: Muna baba here, kana munin'ina?
\v 20 Isu tikati kuna ishe wangu, Tina baba, mutana, nemwana weutana hwavo, mudiki; uye mukoma wake wakafa, zvino iye wasara oga kuna mai vake, uye baba vake vanomuda.
\v 21 Zvino imwi mukati kuvaranda venyu: Burukai naye kwandiri, kuti ndiise meso angu paari.
\v 22 Zvino tikati kuna ishe wangu: Mukomana haangasii baba vake, nokuti kana akasiya baba vake, ivo vachafa.
\v 23 Zvino makati kuvaranda venyu, Kana munin'ina wenyu worugotwe asingaburuki nemi, hamungaonizve chiso changu.
\v 24 Zvino takati takwira kumuranda wenyu, baba vedu, tikavaudza mashoko ashe wedu.
\v 25 Baba vedu vakati, Endaizve, mutitengere zvokudya zvishomanana.
\v 26 Isu tikati, Hatingaburuki, kana munin'ina wedu asingaburuki nesu; nokuti hatingaoni chiso chomurume uya, kana munin'ina wedu asinesu.
\v 27 Muranda wenyu, baba vedu, vakati kwatiri, Munoziva kuti mukadzi wangu akandiberekera vanakomana vaviri;
\v 28 umwe akabva kwandiri, ndikati, Zvirokwazvo akabvamburwa; kubva musi iwoyo handina kuzomuonazve;
\v 29 kana mukanditorera nouyuwo, akawirwa nenjodzi, muchaburutsira vhudzi rangu jena kuguva nokuchema.
\v 30 Naizvozvo, kana zvino ndikanosvika kumuranda wenyu, baba vangu, tisinaiye mukomana, mweya wavo zvawakabatanidzwa nomweya womukomana,
\v 31 vachati kana vachiona kuti mukomana asinesu, vachafa; naizvozvo varanda venyu vachaburutsira vhudzi jena romuranda wenyu, baba vedu, kuguva nokuchema.
\v 32 Nokuti muranda wenyu akazviita rubatso rwomukomana kuna baba vangu, ndikati, Kana ndikasauya naye kwamuri,ini ndichava nemhosva kuna baba vangu nokusingaperi.
\v 33 Naizvozvo zvino ndinokumbira kuti muranda wenyu agare hake ari musungwa washe wangu pachigaro chomukomana, asi mukomana akwire hake navana vababa vake.
\v 34 Nokuti ndingakwira sei kuna baba vangu, ndisina mukomana? Ndirege hangu kuona njodzi ichawira baba vangu.
